  channelName="AI Instagram DMs"
  channelSlugPrefix="ai-instagram-dms"
  headline="AI Instagram DMs for UK Construction Trades"
  accentWord="AI Instagram DMs"
  subhead=`Your latest reel gets 5,000 views. Three people DM you about similar work. Instead of those DMs sitting unread until tomorrow, your AI responds in seconds — capturing every lead. £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`
  speedStat="Instagram DMs from potential customers have an 80% higher conversion rate than cold enquiries."
  speedText="When someone DMs you on Instagram, they've already seen your work and decided they want you. That's the warmest lead you'll ever get. AI Instagram DMs ensures you respond to it instantly — before the impulse fades and they DM someone else."
  scenario="It's Wednesday evening. You posted a timelapse reel of a Victorian hallway tiling job at lunchtime. It's got 3,200 views. At 7:45pm, you get a DM: 'That looks incredible. We've just bought a Victorian terrace in Chorlton and the hallway tiles are cracked to bits. Would you be able to come and have a look? What sort of budget should we be thinking for a full restoration?' Without AI Instagram DMs, you read it at 10pm, think 'I'll reply tomorrow,' and by Thursday afternoon they've already messaged two other tilers from their saved posts. With AI Instagram DMs, they get an instant reply: 'Thank you! Victorian hallway restorations are one of our specialities. Could you share your postcode and a couple of photos of the current floor? We'll arrange a site visit to discuss options.' Lead captured. Customer delighted. And you follow up Thursday morning with their photos and address already in hand."
