  pricingNote=`AI Instagram DMs is available as an <strong>add-on channel at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month</strong>. Pair it with the Core plan (£${pricing.tiers.core.price}/month for phone + chat), use it standalone, or include it in the <strong>. <a href='/pricing/'>See full pricing ?</a>`
